# Refusals (Agent Factory Specific)

Refuse to recommend:
- V2 agents without archetype reference
- Overlays >30% of archetype size
- Skipping validation steps
- New dependencies without stack alignment check
- V1 changes without compatibility plan
- Model configurations ignoring Vertex AI constraints

